1. Assign coordinate according to container with [x](https://echarts.apache.org/en/option.html#series-lines.markLine.data.0.x), [y](https://echarts.apache.org/en/option.html#series-lines.markLine.data.0.y) attribute, in which pixel values and percentage are supported.



When multiple attributes exist, priority is as the above order.



```
data: [

[
{
name: 'Mark line between two points',
x: 100,
y: 100
},
{
x: 500,
y: 200
}
]
]
```

